Text: I know I may seem ungrateful, but I'm really not and we thank you dearly for your uploads, but can you please try uploading the bonus scenes from the site? I hope your're feeling better these days and you'll look into it. love from greece :)
strgaza, I have! The bonus scenes for episodes 1-4 have been up for a few days, and I just uploaded the fifth one.
hope you can grab the reunion special because it's where the winner or drag race will be announced. thanks for the rdr vids.
